&lt;h2 id="01">01&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>杭城的春天很短暂，陈川骑车在路上还能感受到一丝丝凉意。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>路边的花草儿摇头晃脑，红灯也没那么恼人。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>今天走了好多路</title><link>https://bearfly1990.github.io/BF-Hugo/post/diary/2025/12/2025-12-28-dairy/</link><pubDate>Mon, 22 Dec 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://bearfly1990.github.io/BF-Hugo/post/diary/2025/12/2025-12-28-dairy/</guid><description>今天和老婆还有老妈走了好多圈的路</description></item><item><title>Bob家麻将</title><link>https://bearfly1990.github.io/BF-Hugo/post/diary/2025/01/2025-01-31-chusan/</link><pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://bearfly1990.github.io/BF-Hugo/post/diary/2025/01/2025-01-31-chusan/</guid><description>昨天去 Bob 家玩（主要是打麻将），小曼的麻将水平和运气绝对碾压我的。</description></item><item><title>写在乙巳蛇年除夕</title><link>https://bearfly1990.github.io/BF-Hugo/post/diary/2025/01/2025-01-28-before-snake-year/</link><pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://bearfly1990.github.io/BF-Hugo/post/diary/2025/01/2025-01-28-before-snake-year/</guid><description>&lt;p>吃完晚饭，和媳妇去奶奶家呆了一会儿， 走了走，稍微消化了，没那么撑了。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>生命，选择，未来</title><link>https://bearfly1990.github.io/BF-Hugo/post/diary/2025/02/2025-01-28-life-choise-future/</link><pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://bearfly1990.github.io/BF-Hugo/post/diary/2025/02/2025-01-28-life-choise-future/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="引子一">引子（一）&lt;/h2>
&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>楚人有涉江者，其剑自舟中坠于水，遽契其舟曰：“是吾剑之所从坠。”舟止，从其所契者入水求之。舟已行矣，而剑不行，求剑若此，不亦惑乎？（战国·吕不韦《吕氏春秋·察今》）&lt;/p>
&lt;/blockquote></description></item><item><title>2024-12-02</title><link>https://bearfly1990.github.io/BF-Hugo/post/diary/2024/12/2024-12-02-test/</link><pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://bearfly1990.github.io/BF-Hugo/post/diary/2024/12/2024-12-02-test/</guid><description>2012-12-02 Test 好久没有写东西了，有时候想写点什么，也是 ‌ 兴致索然 ‌。
